eName;\n            this.body = body.clone();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public long getLength() {\n            return body.length;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public String getFileName() {\n            return fileName;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public InputStream createInputStream() {\n            return new ByteArrayInputStream(body);\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778689169889}]}
